hopobject.body: In tens, please (ten pound notes) pottsville physiotherapy nsw * On the first Friday morning of almost any other month allthe attention would be focused on two numbers: the latestgovernment estimates for unemployment and job creation. ThisFriday, however, much of the government will be closed. As aresult, the economists and statisticians at the Bureau of LaborStatistics will be at home, and everyone from Fed chairman BenBernanke to thousands of traders will be left without one of themost important clues to the state of the economy.
